<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 09:16:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>骗局中心镇压之后，泰国山区边界上的数千人处于困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-limbo-thai-myanmar-border-after-scam-centre-crackdown-2025-02-24/</link><description>三名消息人士周一告诉路透社，成千上万的外国人从缅甸的在线骗局运营中心被释放在与泰国边界的边界上，在对犯罪团伙经营的化合物的跨国镇压之后。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 07:47:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-limbo-thai-myanmar-border-after-scam-centre-crackdown-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>国家以2000亿美元的自然金融协议进行新的尝试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/countries-make-fresh-attempt-200-billion-nature-finance-deal-2025-02-24/</link><description>本周的各国聚集在罗马，第二次裂开，弄清楚如何每年产生2000亿美元以帮助维护世界的生物多样性 - 并随着美国的回归而射击全球合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 07:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/countries-make-fresh-attempt-200-billion-nature-finance-deal-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>晨价：当德国投票躲避极端时，救济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-02-24/</link><description>看看韦恩·科尔（Wayne Cole）的欧洲和全球市场前一天。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 05:35:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰外交大臣质疑北京访问中国海军活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-foreign-minister-question-chinese-naval-activity-beijing-visit-2025-02-24/</link><description>新西兰的外交部长温斯顿·彼得斯（Winston Peters）将于周二在北京进行为期三天的访问，因为两国之间的关系在中国海军船只在塔斯曼海进行了现场射击演习后紧张。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 04:32:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-foreign-minister-question-chinese-naval-activity-beijing-visit-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾表示，它分享了日本反对单方面尝试重塑全球秩序的事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-it-shares-japans-cause-opposing-unilateral-attempts-reshape-2025-02-24/</link><description>其国防部长周一说，菲律宾与日本有任何单方面试图重塑全球秩序的共同原因。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 03:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-it-shares-japans-cause-opposing-unilateral-attempts-reshape-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>铁矿石因中国钢的更多职责而升高为期四天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/iron-ore-snaps-four-day-rise-due-more-duties-chinese-steel-2025-02-24/</link><description>达利安铁矿石期货价格在周一取得了为期四天的连胜纪录，因为中国钢铁的征收增加了主要的钢材制造成分的需求前景，尽管中国的港口库存减少了秋季。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 03:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/iron-ore-snaps-four-day-rise-due-more-duties-chinese-steel-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球的一周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2025-02-24/</link><description>亚洲足球本周的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 03:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>马斯克的星条链接与中国竞争对手一起统治卫星互联网</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/musks-starlink-races-with-chinese-rivals-dominate-satellite-internet-2025-02-24/</link><description>埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）在太空中的首要地位被北京视为威胁，北京既在竞争对手上投入大量投资，又将军事研究资助了追踪卫星星座的工具。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 03:05:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/musks-starlink-races-with-chinese-rivals-dominate-satellite-internet-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾，日本部长同意进一步增强国防伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-defence-minister-says-discuss-chinas-actions-with-japan-counterpart-2025-02-24/</link><description>日本国防部长中纳卡塔尼（Gen Nakatani）周一说，日本和菲律宾周一同意，面对印度太平洋地区“日益严重”的安全环境，进一步加深了国防联系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 01:26:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-defence-minister-says-discuss-chinas-actions-with-japan-counterpart-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股票期货，德国保持主流</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2025-02-24/</link><description>欧洲股票和周一的欧元攀升，因为德国的选举产生了主流结果，而华尔街期货本周却肯定了AI Diva Nvidia的希望，这将证明技术部门的高价估值。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 00:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-take-record-9-billion-domestic-trips-during-lunar-new-year-xinhua-2025-02-23/</link><description>新华社周日报道，中国在40天的农历新年旅行狂欢中获得了创纪录的90.2亿次国内旅行。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Feb 2025 07:40:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-take-record-9-billion-domestic-trips-during-lunar-new-year-xinhua-2025-02-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国指责澳大利亚“大肆宣传”中国海军演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-accuses-australia-hyping-chinese-naval-drills-2025-02-23/</link><description>中国在澳大利亚和新西兰之间的国际水域进行了直播海军演习。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Feb 2025 05:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-accuses-australia-hyping-chinese-naval-drills-2025-02-23/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰说，中国海军在国际水域举行了第二次直播演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-says-china-failed-explain-inadequate-navy-live-fire-notice-2025-02-22/</link><description>据新西兰广播电台报道，周六的现场直播演习发生在塔斯曼海。</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 03:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-says-china-failed-explain-inadequate-navy-live-fire-notice-2025-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国研究人员发现，蝙蝠病毒通过与Covid相同的途径进入人类细胞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinese-researchers-find-bat-virus-enters-human-cells-via-same-pathway-covid-2025-02-21/</link><description>中国研究人员报道，新发现的蝙蝠冠状病毒使用相同的细胞表面蛋白与导致Covid-19的SARS-COV-2病毒进入人类细胞，从而增加了有一天可能传播给人类的可能性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 22:57:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinese-researchers-find-bat-virus-enters-human-cells-via-same-pathway-covid-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，特朗普政府推出了中国顶级出口政策官员。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-administration-asks-top-china-export-policy-official-resign-sources-say-2025-02-21/</link><description>三名熟悉此事的人说，特朗普政府已迫使一名高级商务部官员负责监督对中国的出口限制。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 22:16:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-administration-asks-top-china-export-policy-official-resign-sources-say-2025-02-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>